---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Simulador PMP® 2026 | Valeria Yashan";
const description = "Practicá para el PMP® con 180 preguntas originales de Valeria Yashan, PMP®. Banco de estudio, simulacro cronometrado, práctica por dominio y casos integrados. ECO 2026.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>

<style>
.sim-wrap { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem; }
.intro-eyebrow { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.09em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #2D6A4F; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center; display: block; }
.intro-title { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.1; text-align: center; }
.intro-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: #6B6B6B; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.7; text-align: center; }
.exam-info-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1.25rem; background: #F2F1EE; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.ei-item { text-align: center; }
.ei-num { display: block; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; }
.ei-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #6B6B6B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.ei-sep { width: 1px; height: 32px; background: #E0DFDB; }
.intro-strategy { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #6B6B6B; background: #E1F5EE; border-left: 3px solid #2D6A4F; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
.intro-strategy strong { color: #2D6A4F; }
.bloque-selector { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.bloque-btn { padding: 6px 14px; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 20px; background: #FAFAF8; color: #6B6B6B; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }
.bloque-btn.active { background: #2D6A4F; border-color: #2D6A4F; color: #fff; }
.bloque-btn:hover:not(.active) { border-color: #2D6A4F; color: #2D6A4F; }
.qty-selector { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.qty-label { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B6B6B; }
.qty-btn { padding: 6px 16px; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 20px; background: #FAFAF8; color: #6B6B6B; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }
.qty-btn.active { background: #2D6A4F; border-color: #2D6A4F; color: #fff; }
.qty-btn:hover:not(.active) { border-color: #2D6A4F; color: #2D6A4F; }
.mode-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0DFDB; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.mode-tab { padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem; border: none; background: none; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; color: #6B6B6B; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -1px; transition: all 0.15s; white-space: nowrap; }
.mode-tab.active { color: #2D6A4F; border-bottom-color: #2D6A4F; font-weight: 600; }
.mode-tab:hover:not(.active) { color: #1A1A1A; }
.dom-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.dom-card { border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.25rem 1rem; background: #FAFAF8; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }
.dom-card:hover { border-color: #2D6A4F; background: #F0FAF5; }
.dom-card.dom-sel { border-color: #2D6A4F; background: #F0FAF5; }
.dom-card .dom-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.dom-card .dom-name { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.dom-card .dom-count { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B6B6B; }
.btn-dom-start { display: block; width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: #2D6A4F; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 0.5rem; transition: background 0.15s; }
.btn-dom-start:hover:not(:disabled) { background: #1B4332; }
.btn-dom-start:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; }
/* HISTORIAL */
.historial-wrap { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
.historial-title { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #6B6B6B; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
.historial-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
.historial-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: #F2F1EE; border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
.historial-item .h-mode { color: #6B6B6B; }
.historial-item .h-score { font-weight: 700; }
.historial-item .h-score.ok { color: #27500A; }
.historial-item .h-score.risk { color: #854F0B; }
.historial-item .h-score.low { color: #A32D2D; }
.historial-item .h-date { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #9B9B9B; }
/* QUIZ */
.intro-hint { text-align: center; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B6B6B; }
.intro-hint a { color: #2D6A4F; }
.quiz-topbar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0DFDB; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-back { background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B6B6B; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; flex-shrink: 0; }
.btn-back:hover { color: #1A1A1A; }
.quiz-mode-label { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: #6B6B6B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
.timer-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; flex-shrink: 0; }
.timer-urgent { color: #A32D2D !important; }
.timer-pace { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #6B6B6B; font-weight: 400; margin-left: 4px; }
.quiz-header { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.quiz-progress-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.q-counter-text { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B6B6B; }
.domain-badge { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
.dom-personas { background: #E1F5EE; color: #0F6E56; }
.dom-proceso { background: #EEEDFE; color: #3C3489; }
.dom-entorno { background: #FAEEDA; color: #854F0B; }
.progress-bar { width: 100%; height: 4px; background: #E0DFDB; border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
.progress-fill { height: 100%; background: #2D6A4F; border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.35s ease; }
.quiz-meta { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; align-items: center; }
.meta-pill { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; color: #6B6B6B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
.dif-avanzada { background: #FCEBEB; border-color: #F7C1C1; color: #A32D2D; }
.dif-intermedia { background: #FAEEDA; border-color: #FAC775; color: #854F0B; }
.dif-basica { background: #EAF3DE; border-color: #C0DD97; color: #3B6D11; }
.meta-multiple { background: #EEEDFE; border-color: #CECBF6; color: #3C3489; }
.meta-caso { background: #F3E5F5; border-color: #CE93D8; color: #6A1B9A; }
/* BOTÓN MARCAR */
.btn-marcar { background: none; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px 9px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; color: #6B6B6B; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; transition: all 0.15s; margin-left: auto; }
.btn-marcar:hover { border-color: #E67E22; color: #E67E22; }
.btn-marcar.marcada { background: #FFF3E0; border-color: #E67E22; color: #E67E22; }
/* CASO INTEGRADO */
.caso-context { background: #F3E5F5; border: 1px solid #CE93D8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #1A1A1A; }
.caso-context-title { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #6A1B9A; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.caso-sub-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6A1B9A; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.question-text { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; white-space: pre-line; }
.multiple-hint { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #3C3489; background: #EEEDFE; border: 1px solid #CECBF6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 12px; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: none; }
.options-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0; }
.feedback-box { padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border: 1px solid; }
.fb-ok { background: #EAF3DE; border-color: #97C459; }
.fb-err { background: #FCEBEB; border-color: #F09595; }
.fb-header { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
.fb-ok .fb-header { color: #27500A; }
.fb-err .fb-header { color: #791F1F; }
.fb-body { font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #1A1A1A; }
.quiz-actions { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 10px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.quiz-actions-right { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
.btn-confirm { padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: #2D6A4F; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
.btn-confirm:hover:not(:disabled) { background: #1B4332; }
.btn-confirm:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; }
.btn-next { padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: #2D6A4F; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
.btn-next:hover { background: #1B4332; }
/* RESULTADO */
.result-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.result-pct { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 4.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: #2D6A4F; line-height: 1; }
.result-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: #6B6B6B; margin-top: 4px; }
.result-mode { display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #6B6B6B; }
.result-msg { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #6B6B6B; line-height: 1.65; background: #F2F1EE; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
.domain-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.domain-card { background: #F2F1EE; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; }
.d-name { font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: #6B6B6B; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.d-pct { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.d-diag { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; }
.diag-ok { color: #27500A; }
.diag-risk { color: #854F0B; }
.diag-low { color: #A32D2D; }
.result-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-retry { padding: 0.7rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 6px; background: #FAFAF8; color: #1A1A1A; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; }
.btn-retry:hover { background: #F2F1EE; }
.btn-incorrectas { padding: 0.7rem 1.25rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: #1B4332; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; display: none; }
.btn-incorrectas:hover { background: #0f2820; }
.btn-marcadas { padding: 0.7rem 1.25rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: #E67E22; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; display: none; }
.btn-marcadas:hover { background: #CA6F1E; }
.btn-switch { padding: 0.7rem 1.25rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: #2D6A4F; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
.btn-switch:hover { background: #1B4332; }
.result-ctas { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-libro { padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #2D6A4F; border-radius: 6px; color: #2D6A4F; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-libro:hover { background: #E1F5EE; }
.btn-consulta { padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 6px; color: #6B6B6B; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-consulta:hover { background: #F2F1EE; color: #1A1A1A; }

/* INSTRUCTIVO COLAPSABLE */
.instructivo-wrap { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #E0DFDB; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
.instructivo-toggle { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; width: 100%; padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; background: #F2F1EE; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; text-align: left; transition: background 0.15s; }
.instructivo-toggle:hover { background: #E1F5EE; }
.instructivo-toggle .toggle-icon { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B6B6B; transition: transform 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0; }
.instructivo-toggle.open .toggle-icon { transform: rotate(180deg); }
.instructivo-body { display: none; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; background: white; }
.instructivo-body.open { display: block; }
.inst-section { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.inst-section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.inst-section-title { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #2D6A4F; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
.inst-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 8px; }
.inst-card { background: #F2F1EE; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }
.inst-card .ic-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.inst-card .ic-title { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.inst-card .ic-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B6B6B; line-height: 1.5; }
.inst-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
.inst-list li { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #1A1A1A; line-height: 1.55; display: flex; gap: 8px; }
.inst-list li::before { content: "→"; color: #2D6A4F; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
.inst-tip { background: #E1F5EE; border-left: 3px solid #2D6A4F; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #1A1A1A; line-height: 1.55; }
.inst-tip strong { color: #2D6A4F; }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .inst-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .domain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .dom-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .ei-sep { display: none; }
  .result-actions, .result-ctas { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; text-align: center; }
  .mode-tab { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.6rem; }
}
</style>

<div class="sim-wrap">

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <div id="s-intro">
    <span class="intro-eyebrow">Simulador gratuito · ECO 2026</span>
    <h1 class="intro-title">Practicá para el PMP®</h1>
    <p class="intro-desc">180 preguntas originales del <em>Tomo III — Simulacros de Práctica Intensiva</em>. Distribución real ECO: Personas · Proceso · Entorno de negocio.</p>

    <div class="exam-info-bar">
      <div class="ei-item"><span class="ei-num">180</span><span class="ei-label">preguntas en el examen</span></div>
      <div class="ei-sep"></div>
      <div class="ei-item"><span class="ei-num">230</span><span class="ei-label">minutos disponibles</span></div>
      <div class="ei-sep"></div>
      <div class="ei-item"><span class="ei-num">~AT</span><span class="ei-label">puntaje mínimo</span></div>
      <div class="ei-sep"></div>
      <div class="ei-item"><span class="ei-num">Sin</span><span class="ei-label">penalización por error</span></div>
    </div>


    <!-- INSTRUCTIVO COLAPSABLE -->
    <div class="instructivo-wrap">
      <button class="instructivo-toggle" id="inst-toggle" onclick="toggleInstructivo()">
        <span>¿Cómo funciona este simulador?</span>
        <span class="toggle-icon">▼</span>
      </button>
      <div class="instructivo-body" id="inst-body">

        <div class="inst-section">
          <div class="inst-section-title">Modos disponibles</div>
          <div class="inst-grid">
            <div class="inst-card">
              <div class="ic-icon">📖</div>
              <div class="ic-title">Banco de estudio</div>
              <div class="ic-desc">Feedback inmediato después de cada respuesta. Elegís cuántas preguntas y de qué capítulo. Ideal para aprender y detectar brechas.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="inst-card">
              <div class="ic-icon">⏱</div>
              <div class="ic-title">Simulacro</div>
              <div class="ic-desc">Sin feedback hasta el final. Cronometrado igual que el examen real (230 min para 120 preguntas). Resultado con diagnóstico por dominio ECO.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="inst-card">
              <div class="ic-icon">🎯</div>
              <div class="ic-title">Por dominio</div>
              <div class="ic-desc">Practicá solo Personas, Proceso o Entorno de Negocio. Sin tiempo límite. Feedback inmediato. Para trabajar brechas específicas.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="inst-card">
              <div class="ic-icon">📋</div>
              <div class="ic-title">Casos integrados</div>
              <div class="ic-desc">5 escenarios extendidos con 2–3 subpreguntas encadenadas, igual al examen real. El contexto del caso aparece en todas las subpreguntas.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="inst-section">
          <div class="inst-section-title">Funciones de estudio</div>
          <ul class="inst-list">
            <li><strong>☆ Marcar para repasar</strong> — marcá cualquier pregunta durante el quiz. Después podés practicar solo las marcadas desde el Banco → "Marcadas".</li>
            <li><strong>Repasar incorrectas</strong> — al terminar una sesión aparece el botón para repasar solo las que fallaste, en modo simulacro.</li>
            <li><strong>Solo mis incorrectas</strong> — en la pestaña Simulacro podés iniciar un simulacro cronometrado solo con tus incorrectas de la sesión anterior.</li>
            <li><strong>Ritmo por pregunta</strong> — en el simulacro el timer muestra cuántos segundos tenés por pregunta restante para llegar a tiempo.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="inst-section">
          <div class="inst-section-title">Mi progreso</div>
          <ul class="inst-list">
            <li>La pestaña <strong>Mi progreso</strong> guarda automáticamente tus últimas 20 sesiones con fecha, modo y puntaje.</li>
            <li>Muestra tu <strong>precisión total acumulada</strong> y cuántas preguntas respondiste en total.</li>
            <li>Los datos se guardan en tu navegador. No se comparten ni se pierden al cerrar la página.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="inst-section">
          <div class="inst-section-title">Contenido del simulador</div>
          <ul class="inst-list">
            <li><strong>180 preguntas originales</strong> del Tomo III de la serie de certificación PMP® de Valeria Yashan.</li>
            <li><strong>Cap. 22 (60 preguntas)</strong>: 20 Personas · 25 Proceso · 15 Entorno de negocio.</li>
            <li><strong>Cap. 23 (120 preguntas)</strong>: 40 Personas · 49 Proceso · 31 Entorno de negocio.</li>
            <li>Tipos de ítem: Situacional · Conceptual · Cálculo · Respuesta múltiple · Ordenamiento · Relacionar columnas · Caso integrado.</li>
            <li>Dificultad: Básica (○) · Intermedia (·) · Avanzada (★).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="inst-tip">
          <strong>Estrategia recomendada:</strong> empezá por el Banco de estudio con 20 preguntas al azar para calibrar tu nivel. Luego practicá por dominio en los que estés bajo 70%. Cuando llegues a 80% en los tres dominios, hacé el simulacro completo de 120 preguntas cronometrado.
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="intro-strategy"><strong>Estrategia recomendada:</strong> empezá con el banco de preguntas para identificar tus brechas por dominio. Cuando llegues al 80% en los tres dominios, pasá al simulacro cronometrado de 120 preguntas.</p>

    <!-- TABS -->
    <div class="mode-tabs">
      <button class="mode-tab active" id="tab-banco" onclick="switchTab('banco')">📖 Banco</button>
      <button class="mode-tab" id="tab-simulacro" onclick="switchTab('simulacro')">⏱ Simulacro</button>
      <button class="mode-tab" id="tab-dominio" onclick="switchTab('dominio')">🎯 Por dominio</button>
      <button class="mode-tab" id="tab-casos" onclick="switchTab('casos')">📋 Casos integrados</button>
